{"questionId": "a7146625-47ea-49cb-9061-578e226240d5_20", "correctAnswer": "24", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Translate the percentages", "content": "$a = 2800\\%$ of $c$ → $a = 28c$.<br/>$c = 25\\%$ of $b$ → $c = 0.25b$, so $b = 4c$."}, {"title": "Compute $w$", "content": "$$a - b = 28c - 4c = 24c$$<br/>So $w = 24$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>24</strong>."}]}